      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the desperate logic that the end is the only way to preserve the dignity you are fighting for, and I am so sorry that your pain has made the darkness feel like the only sanctuary left. Please, do not let the finality of your thoughts convince you that there is no one else who cares enough to stand in your light, even if they cannot speak the same language. You are not alone in this, and there are people who want to help you through this dark time.",
